headline: Has Amex’s 2025 Surge Outrun Its Earnings Power?
summary: If you are wondering whether American Express is still worth buying after its huge run, or if you have already missed the boat, this breakdown will help you decide whether the current price actually makes sense. The stock has climbed 3.7% over the last week, 4.0% over the past month, and is now up around 29.0% year to date and 29.5% over the last year. headline: Western Alliance Bancorporation Appoints Two New Board Members
summary: PHOENIX, December 11, 2025--Western Alliance Bancorporation (NYSE: WAL) today announced the appointment of two distinguished leaders to its Board of Directors, adding sizable expertise in the key areas of cybersecurity and risk management as the organization nears the $100 billion asset threshold.
